response.overview: Ajinkya true to its name, celebrates triumph against all odds. It's the story of a dynamic entrepreneur named Ajinkya, spearheading Midas Touch, his rapidly expanding construction company.He is confident, aggressive and shrewd, leaving no stone unturned in his quest to get what he wants, even if it means resorting to unethical means to achieve it.
response.tagline: Ajinkya true to its name, celebrates triumph against all odds.
response.title: Ajinkya
